- hw/core/machine.c

  Downstream does not have hw_compat_10_2. Make sure that machine types
  prior to RHEL 9.8 default to migrate-pr=off.

- hw/scsi/scsi-disk.c

  Downstream is missing commit 40de712a89d8f ("migration: Add
  error-parameterized function variants in VMSD struct"), so add a
  .post_load() wrapper function that reports the Error and returns
